features: [Items Included]There are 8 different items, including three packing cubes (M + L + XL), one underwear bag, one toiletry bag, one shoe bag, one laundry bag and one zipper bag.You can choose to purchase ExploreBliss Packing Cubes with different combinations of pieces and sets according to your own needs. The ExploreBliss Packing Cubes are very lightweight, to keep your luggage organize without adding to the weight of your bags.

[Multiple Sizes]8 set packing cube sets come with different sizes, including packing cubes（Extra Large：17.48''×12.13''×3.98''; Large: 13.78''×12.73''×3.98''; Medium: 13.78''×9.72''×3.98''), underwear bag (12.60''×9.06''×4.72''), shoe bag (16.93''×9.06''×4.72''), laundry bag (14.17''×10.63''), toiletry bag (8.66''×5.51''×3.15''), zipper bag (10.63''×6.30'').These packing cubes for travel can easily fit into commonly used 20 inch, 24 inch, or 28 inch suitcases.

[Convenient Design] The zipper of ExploreBliss packing cubes is an upgraded zipper for a strong, smooth zipper function. While the underwear bag has a design to protect your privacy, the clothes storage bags have clear panels so that you may quickly find a specific clothing item.

[Organized Packing and Space Saving] Multiple sizes of packing cubes with different functions are available for you to choose from to separate your different clothes. Save time for your trip, travel or outdoor activities by avoiding misplacing different items. The mesh netting of travel bags also allows you to pick out what you want easily and to save space in your suitcase with proper organization.

[Multi Functional Packing Cubes] ExploreBliss packing cubes include contents for different purposes. The packing cubes can help reduce wrinkles in your clothes by preventing movement inside your suitcase. Not only can they be used for family travel, but they are also ideal for business trips, outdoor camping and daily storage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lightweight and you can put a lot in each bags.
reviews.reviewText: The items came on time and delivered with care. These bags; organizers are great when it comes to having all your items all in tacked and well organized. These bags comes in other colors, I got the gray one! They are lightweight so they will not add too much weight in your luggage. The material is thin but strong enough to hold your things. If you want these to last long. I do will say not over stuff these bags. Like if your struggling to close it because it's a lot of stuff. Don't! You know, use common sense!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Convenient, durable ,flexible and light storages cubes!
reviews.reviewText: Hi Joyce .I find the product to be extremely helpful . I travel back and forth to many locations for different occasions amd events during the week. I go to Work 2 times per week. Then after work I usually workout or connect with friends and family. I am now traveling to many different locations 5 to 7 days per week.These storage cubes are very light and airy and flexible . I use them for clothes and for accessories. They are very durable and have held up even when they were filled to capacity. The zippers are easy easy to use and glide very easily and have not gotten stuck. I also use the small cubes for makeup and the shoe bag protects my clothes when I am carrying a change of shoes regularly. The set came with a variety of sizes and shapes. I liked everything about the product.Overall I would recommend this product to to my friends, coworkers and family

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Served the purpose.
reviews.reviewText: I bought 3 sets of these to take on a cruise. They did help us to keep our clothing more organized, however some of the bags soon had slight tears in them. Not the most durable to use over and over.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars you get what you pay for
reviews.reviewText: Note that these are packing cubes with no compression. So they'll keep your bags organized but won't free up space like compression cubes do. One of the cubes ripped on our first trip. It wasn't even fully packed. So quality is definitely on the very low end side. That said, for the price it's still nice to keep clothes organized when traveling and you can just toss when the cubes break.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best pack organizers EVER!!
reviews.reviewText: These are my favorite packing organisers!! Some big standout features are the mesh on the top so you can see what’s on the inside easily, the number and size of bags so you can be organized for a week to 10 days and yet fit back into small storage bag, the smooth zippers, and the bags u zip on 3 sides so you can lay the flap all the way back to pack easily. Love this set!!! This is what I packed… I’m larger so most people could fit more and I had extra room in most bags.Bag 1: 1 pair of jeans, 7 pair of capris/leggings, 1 swimsuit. Bag 2: 8 shirts. Bag 3: 2 light pullovers, 2 pairs of pajamas. Bag 4: a jewelry travel case. Bag 5 (actually the set storage bag but I’m using it!!!): an accessories travel. Bag 6 (Shoe bag): pair of tennis shoes, pair of flip flops. Bag 7: 3 long socks 6 ankle socks, 8 underwear, 5 bras. Bag 8 (Stuff bag): sunglasses, cosmetic travel bag, Advil, charger box, Trash Pandas game, and medication case for a week. I would definitely recommend these for any traveler!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Great price, poor quality
reviews.reviewText: Great price, but you definitely get what you pay for. The zipper on the largest organizer (of the 8 pc set) had to be zipped all the way around and then unzipped in order to correct a gap in the zipper track.While packing it to use the day after receiving it, the same largest organizer developed a hole near the handle. The organizer was only half full at the time.The organizers are all paper thin. Maybe good for packing baby clothes, not suitable and reliable for even lightweight adult size clothing

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for packing cubes for an upcoming trip and these are going to be perfect. This set offers a nice variety of sizes and they are sturdy material.
